metadata.name: Behrouz x DiscoShark #001
metadata.title: Behrouz x DiscoShark - AR
metadata.description: Behrouz x DiscoShark is a collab between Behrouz, Kevin McHugh (creator of DiscoShark), and IMMUSE that pays homage to Behrouz’s famous Miami nightclub, Do Not Sit On The Furniture, and celebrates all the great friends, family, DJ’s and musicians that are supporting Behrouz and his family in his time of need. This Visual Single features an unreleased track co-produced by Behrouz and El Mundo in 2021 while Behrouz was on tour playing shows in Amsterdam and around the Netherlands. Tribal yet Gregorian, intense in all the right ways, moody, dark…music you’d rave to in an underwater cavern club. The AR scene immerses you in a version of the Do Not Sit club as if it were a natural music cathedral sunken beneath the ocean. The scene opens underneath the famous Spaceship ceiling lights, surrounded by pillars of kelp, like an undersea Sagrada Familia. Venus oversees the action from her oyster shell, and DiscoShark patrols the dance floor.
